<h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">What is a cookie?</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">A cookie is a small piece of data that a website stores on your device when you visit, typically containing information about the website itself, a unique identifier that allows the site to recognise your web browser when you return, additional data that serves the purpose of the cookie, and the lifespan of the cookie itself.</span></p>
